  "playingCareerSummary": "Former India left-handed all-rounder: 3 ODIs (2009). Long domestic career with Mumbai. Played in the IPL for Mumbai Indians, Kings XI Punjab, Pune Warriors and Rajasthan Royals. Widely regarded as one of the best batting mentors in Indian cricket — credited as a key influence in Rohit Sharma's and KL Rahul's development.",
